

	 
      aah! in laakposhte binavaa! saalhaast be posht oftaade,va daasto paa mizane.hamash kaalasho in var o oonvar mikone va dast o paasho too hava tekoon mide.gahi benazaram sahneye mozheki myad,her her mikhandam.vaaghean ke mozheke.vali bishtare oghat delam barash misooze.baba bargard dige!chera pas nemitooni becharkhi? khandam az beyn mire.hala dige ba narahati negash mikonam,laakposhte binava!hataa yek lahze ham az talash dast bar nemidare.pas chera nemytooni becharkhi laanati?chera hanooz kale paaiii? han? taghsir az laake. are,in laake bozorge sangin.hamooni ke toosh ghayem mishi,hamooni ke hamash bayad roye badanet bekeshish,hamishe,bedoone vaghfe.va cheghadr bayad kond harekat koni.cheghadr aaheste,engaar ta abad bayad rah beri,va gahi ham toosh ghayem shi.agar kesi az laaket begiratet,bichareii,dast o paa mizani,vali kesi ke az laaket to ro boland kone,hich nemitooni moghavemat koni mage na?...aah! aslan khandedar nist.man didam ke hata myshe be posht rooye laaket becharkhonanet,tond,kheili tond,va to ba inke miri too laaket ghayem mishi,vali bahash micharkhi,...bayad becharkhi...hataa esmetam az laak e mordeshoor bordadt ke in hame mokafat dare root gozashtan LAAk---posht....  "khob koochooloye khoshgelam,ghand o asalam,begoo gorbe chi mige? "meje myoo myoo" "affarin golam,hala begoo sage chi mige?" "mije vagh vagh" "affarin joojeye bahoosham."......  amma haregz kasi behem yad nadad laakposhte chi mige.laakposht,dar skoot,oon laake mordeshoor bordasho mikeshe. che saboor. va man midoonam,age kasi ziad harf nemizane,baraye in nist ke khodesho migire,ya aadame bymazeiie,ya hosele nadare,...na, oon faghat dare yek laake laanati ro bezoor bedoosh mikeshe.  
    
